Saratoga OverviewOperations




Saratoga Resources, Inc. is an independent E&P company engaged in the production, development, acquisition and exploitation of crude oil and natural gas properties with assets on state/parish leases in the shallow transition zone in Louisiana state waters and shallow Gulf of Mexico.

   hover responsive    Ship Shoal 78 top1 #a1262b   Vermilion 153 top1 #a1262b   Lake Fortuna top1 #a1262b   Little Bay/SAB top1 #a1262b 





