Our LeadersExecutive Management






 


Randal McDonald, Jr.
Controller
Mr. McDonald has served as Saratoga’s Controller since November 2011. Previously, from 2007 to 2011, Mr. McDonald served as Controller of Baseline Oil & Gas Corp., an independent oil and gas company.
