Saratoga Resources Inc.


            
            Saratoga Resources, Inc. is an independent exploration and production company, which engages in the production, development, acquisition and exploitation of natural gas and crude oil properties. The company was founded by Thomas F. Cooke on July 25, 1990 and is headquartered in Houston, TX.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 
   






   



























